{"tid":1255892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實掟雞蛋已經令好多人反感, 再搞落去只會冇晒民意...","createTime":"2019-06-24T16:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T01:25:13.000Z","uid":267498,"like":118,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"76bc98f9c43a0de5907adf3d260d0f7e3d5843ef","tid":1255892,"uid":267498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:54:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌啦 開口埋口就民意逆轉<br />\n與其說服我地唔好衝<br />\n不如諗下點樣教化「黃絲」<br />\n令佢地逐步認同</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>抗爭係可以升級</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n長遠計<br />\n政府一路漠視民意<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">行動向各個方向升級都係無可避免</span></strong><br />\n（人數、範圍、程度）<br />\n與其下下擔心民意逆轉<br />\n不如先教化民意<br />\n深化「黃絲」對政府嘅怨恨<br />\n等佢地明白「和平」喺呢個政府面前<br />\n係幾咁無用，幾咁垃圾，幾咁 R 痕<br />\n從而合理化勇武行為<br />\n<br />\n廢話少講<br />\n用圖交代 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ttTfS5r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FttTfS5r.png&h=fe4185b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jSyjAiN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjSyjAiN.png&h=74be4cac&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oFySViO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoFySViO.png&h=03cad89e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nFB <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/吾講吾德-389239205027484/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%E5%90%BE%E8%AC%9B%E5%90%BE%E5%BE%B7-389239205027484%2F&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRkVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=514c43b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/吾講吾德-389239205027484/</a><br />\nIG <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/knowtalk_knowduck/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fknowtalk_knowduck%2F&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRkVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=67b30b13\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/knowtalk_knowduck/</a><br />\nTG <a href=\"https://t.me/knowtalk_knowduck\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fknowtalk_knowduck&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRkVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=b4b1ca14\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/knowtalk_knowduck</a><br />\n<br />\n用詩書同矯情推廣勇武<br />\n拉近和理非同勇武嘅距離<br />\n<strong>歡迎偷圖 cap 圖 air drop 放送</strong><br />\n三個平台同步推廣，歡迎供稿<br />\n<br />\n諗三個已經好撚極限下<br />\n啲學養已經還返晒俾中學阿 sir<br />\n跪求中化撚提供更多 idea<br />\n<del>唔係講笑，真係諗多個都諗唔到</del><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bea1de226223fc4475d86e7e53f240ac4ff5257","tid":1255892,"uid":267498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:56:03.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n同埋有冇中化巴打可以幫手諗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c0ac3f5fa278da6ba56e93de216cc3b315eb13","tid":1255892,"uid":201902,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T17:00:46.000Z","msg":"掟個雞蛋唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb606624425bd6bb9d49e2e37fe08fca782971a","tid":1255892,"uid":201902,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"02c0ac3f5fa278da6ba56e93de216cc3b315eb13","tid":1255892,"uid":201902,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T17:00:46.000Z","msg":"掟個雞蛋唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T17:00:56.000Z","msg":"都*"}